intro: The later version of Good Morning Ms. Bliss, the show was moved from Disney to NBC. The only characters from the GMMB that went on to Saved by the Bell were Xach Morris, Screech Powers and Lisa Turtle. In addition, Zach's long time neighbor, Jessie Spano joins the gang. New Student A.C. Slater joins the gang as well. Zach's long time crush Kelly Kapowski, comes into Bayside High School. This gang of six faces life with their problems. Several include Zach being in detention, to Screech winning a chess match against their arch enemy. The show follows the gang throughout the four years of high school. However, druing the senior year, Kelly and Jessie decided to leave the show. This occured after only half of the episodes have been shot. With still another half a season left, the gang welcomes Tori Scott, Zach's new girlfriend. In the Tori series, the gang comes up with new school songs, and Mrs. Belding, yes Mr. Belding's wife bear a child. The show closes with the seperation of the grauduating class of Bayside High School. The show then continues to Saved by the Bell, The College Years Written by Saved by the bell {savedbythebell@maiwebsite.cjb.net}
